<div id="review_2452189747" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2452189747" />
    <a title="Patty Lauren" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/69411887-patty-lauren"><img alt="Patty Lauren" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1619439015p2/69411887.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2452189747?book_show_action=true">Jul 10, 2018</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Patty Lauren" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Patty Lauren" href="/user/show/69411887-patty-lauren">Patty Lauren</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2452189747" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12059814750535091969">We saw the movie, “Adrift”, and I wanted to read the book after finding out it was based on a true story. Her bravery and perseverance despite what happened and how long she was at sea was inspiring to read!</span>

          </span>
        </div>


