<span id="freeTextContainer12497406327630030439">I can imagine that all the details about the boat and the sailing, can mean a lot to people who sail. But she lost me in all those numbers. But nevertheless, it is a must-read. This book made me cry a couple of times. I really felt bad for her that the parents of Richard weren’t really open towards her and that the brother-in-law didn’t include her for Richard’s boat. But I guess you can’t really know from Tami’s perspective how his family mourned.</span>

